title: DAZ3D - Gianni 7 Pro Bundle plus Extras
description:
Resurrecting another of my previous Ups...

GIANNI 7 PRO BUNDLE (plus Extras)
---------------------------------

This bundle includes:


Gianni 7
--------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/85f2a75b7970a9b3e9050dae4630bf13.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23794

Daz is excited to welcome Gianni 7 to the Genesis 3 family. Gianni is a handcrafted character with intricate details that truly bring to life his realistic, life-like features. Gianni 7 has a muscular and defined, chiseled physique. He is not only handsome but warm and charming as well. Whether he is a modern day super hero, an expert in espionage or a descendant of royalty, Gianni 7 encompasses what it means to truly be a hero and leading man. Gianni 7 is universally attractive, all the while maintaining a super strong and masculine appeal with his squared jaw and classically handsome face, making him an excellent addition to any scene and render.


FWSA Cole HD for Gianni 7
-------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/1675662cb9ca2f85a230d080c3fd3ec6.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/24023

Cole is a high quality character for Gianni 7 for use in Daz Studio 4.8 and up. The head and body are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. Please Note: While Cole was designed with Daz Studio 4.8 in mind, and its amazing Iray render engine, He will also work and look great using the 3Delight render engine!


Gray for Gianni 7
-----------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/e71b2dcc7ea5dfa6bba08ecc77f3e5ba.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/24029

Gray is a ruggedly handsome new character for Gianni 7. 
Gray includes Custom Sculpted HD Head and Body Morphs to give Gianni 7 a unique new look. Gray includes 6 eye colors and a custom chest tattoo. The skin was crafted from high-res photos and the textures are based on Genesis 3 Male Base UV maps.


Adam Hair for G3M
-----------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/58ba549dbc5b8085b18ec805dac11659.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23911

Adam Hair is a modern classic hairstyle for the Genesis 3 Male(s). Its sleek layered look and style expansions take this hair from sophisticated to edgy in a dial setting. Short choppy layers are combined with a contemporary no-fuss look; a combination which creates an effortlessly masculine razor cut style. From the board room to the battle field, this hair will suit a multitude of Genesis 3 Male scenarios. Adam Hair includes 20 Color settings, with individual maps created for each, in both Iray and 3Delight options as well as six specific Shape Styles and 26 Adjustment and Fit settings for additional ease of use.


Finlay Hair (G2M and G3M)
--------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/98df6aaaa1cdd3d00f02cac4a0156897.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23110

Finlay Hair is a slicked back long men's haircut. It is fitted for Genesis 2 Male(s) and Genesis 3 Male(s) (.DUF) with custom auto-conforming morphs for DAZ Original characters. Iray and 3Delight material presets for various texture map colors are included plus diffuse color setting samples. For Genesis 2 figures in Poser, optimized material presets are also included. The diffuse color samples show how you can easily create your own tints by changing the diffuse color of the hair. Note: For Genesis 2 figures in Poser, this product is compatible via the DSON Importer for Poser.


DA Granite Poses for Gianni 7
-----------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/33181b8df685c3358477111dfc754e74.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23849

A set of 20 carefully crafted, hard as granite poses for Gianni 7 and Genesis 3 Male(s). So strike a pose with Genesis 3 and this set of bold poses designed to show off the beautiful bends of the Genesis 3 Figures.


Capsces Tough as Nails Poses and Expressions for Gianni 7
---------------------------------------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/236d933bb506609e1764c03a2d56cb8c.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23933

A great set of general purpose Capsces poses with a tough guy, bodybuilder bent. Includes expressions to pump up the look.
